"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-29-triple-gold-medalist-blasts-olympic-village-conditions-paris-2024-21319323\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Ariarne Titmus may have already won a gold medal atParis2024, but she says that is despite the difficult conditions at theOlympicVillage.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian is now a triple gold medallist after her two triumphs at Tokyo 2021 and has won five Olympic medals in total.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 139, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9519018569542555e-22, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 211, \"end\": 216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6179460365357766, \"rank\": 0.6182062416483745, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the 400m freestyle champion is not impressed with what the athletes are dealing with in Paris when it comes to their living conditions.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999937558641, \"rank\": 6.244190532351311e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won the 400m freestyle on Saturday, but was disappointed that she could not break her own world record in the process.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It probably wasn't the time I thought I was capable of, but living in the Olympic Village makes it hard to perform,' Titmus said on Sunday.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.159787889771958e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's definitely not made for high performance, so it's about who can really keep it together in the mind.'\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The cardboard beds in the Olympic villagehave come in for heavy criticism, with a number of athletes complaining about how uncomfortable the recyclable beds are,while the food being served has also proved unpopular.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian former Olympic swimmer James Magnussen has spoken out about the problems and feels athletes will be badly hampered by the conditions.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.998394228672673, \"rank\": 0.0015615849659880116, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Magnussen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is multiple factors that make village life far from ideal,' Magnussen wrote in hiscolumn for the Australian Daily Telegraph.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.998394228672673, \"rank\": 0.0015615849659880116, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's the cardboard beds, which can not give you optimal sleep.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's the no airconditioning, which is going to play a bigger factor as the week goes.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was 20 degrees and raining yesterday.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be mid 30s in the coming days.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's going to play a factor and the Australian team having their own portable air conditioners will be a welcome relief.'\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9435748540379552, \"rank\": 0.050385818369733416, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added on the Matty & The Missile podcast: 'There will be many athletes across the two weeks of competition who miss out on a medal\\u2026 because they are unsettled by this new environment.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have not seen this at an Olympic games before.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have not had this amount of complaints about a village in Olympics history.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We saw again tonight great results in the pool but as far as times goes, they are well off those world (record) marks.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not think it's a slow pool.\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's sleeping on cardboard beds\\u2026 At the end of the day, it's about who can overcome these setbacks, who can put these distractions aside.'\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Swimming head coach, Rohan Taylor, is not on board with the complaints, and says conditions are all part of the challenge.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2260, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohan_Taylor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rohan Taylor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohan_Taylor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohan_Taylor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Olympics has always been a challenge.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every Olympics I have been a part of, every Olympic Games that you see, is a test of athletes' ability to come here, compete and perform when it matters,' he said.\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's about how you manage yourself and whatever environments are presented, whatever the beds are, whatever the food is, everybody deals with it.'\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Olympics has always been this way and that's the way it is.\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's and that's the beauty of it.'\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Adam Peaty tests positive for Covid with relays still to come at Paris 2024  ArrowMORE:Team GB star Tom Pidcock responds to boos from French fans after clinching Olympic gold  ArrowMORE:Inside Tom Daley's private life, his age-gap marriage and children  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2991, \"end\": 3001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 3091, \"end\": 3102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Pidcock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\"}, {\"begin\": 3125, \"end\": 3131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9841111204581237, \"rank\": 0.013684614390717163, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3184, \"end\": 3193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0060906413059193e-36, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3551, \"end\": 3557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3855, \"entities\": []}]}"